or:#555555;\">주소</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">또는</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">거소가</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">분명하지</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">않거나</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">외국</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">거주자의</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">경우에는</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">민사소송법상의</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">관할법원에</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">제기합니다</span><span lang=\"en-us\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">.<br></span><span lang=\"en-us\" style=\"font-size:9pt;color:#555555;\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">②</span><span lang=\"en-us\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\" xml:lang=\"en-us\"> \"</span><span style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:\'굴림\';color:#555555;\">몰</span><span lang=\"en-us\" style=\"font-size:9pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#555555;\" xml:lang=\"en-us\">\"</span><span style=\"font-size: